10880220@unknown@formal@none@1@S@This Overall Analysis System for Intelligence Support (OASIS) integrates among the most advanced text analytics and text mining technologies available on today's market.@1@23@@oe@30-11-2008
10880230@unknown@formal@none@1@S@This system led Europol to make the most significant progress to support law enforcement objectives at the international level.@1@19@@oe@30-11-2008
