10880670@unknown@formal@none@1@S@==Implications==@1@1@@oe@30-11-2008
10880680@unknown@formal@none@1@S@Until recently websites most often used text-based lexical searches; in other words, users could find documents only by the words that happened to occur in the documents.@1@27@@oe@30-11-2008
