10901820@unknown@formal@none@1@S@OLIF is an open, XML-compliant standard for the exchange of terminological and lexical data.@1@14@@oe@30-11-2008
10901830@unknown@formal@none@1@S@Although originally intended as a means for the exchange of lexical data between proprietary machine translation lexicons, it has evolved into a more general standard for terminology exchange.@1@28@@oe@30-11-2008
10901840@unknown@formal@none@1@S@<span id="anchor_xliff"></span>@1@2@@oe@30-11-2008
10901850@unknown@formal@none@1@S@===XLIFF===@1@1@@oe@30-11-2008
