10901870@unknown@formal@none@1@S@It is intended to provide a single interchange file format that can be understood by any localization provider.@1@18@@oe@30-11-2008
10901880@unknown@formal@none@1@S@XLIFF is the preferred way of exchanging data in XML format in the translation industry.@1@15@@oe@30-11-2008
10901890@unknown@formal@none@1@S@===TransWS===@1@1@@oe@30-11-2008
